This file is a placeholder marker. The actual placeholder.zip must be created by the CI/CD pipeline
before running terraform apply. Use the following command:

  cd modules/aws/lambda
  echo "placeholder" > /tmp/placeholder.py
  zip placeholder.zip -j /tmp/placeholder.py

The Lambda source_code_hash and filename attributes are set to ignore_changes in the lifecycle block,
so the CI/CD pipeline can deploy actual function code without Terraform managing it.
